                    </div>
                    <div class="payment-grid-element mercadopago">
                        <img src="https://testingsite.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/5_logo-color-fondo-blanco-correcto@3x-15cafca6.png" alt="">
                        <p>1.Transferir dinero<br>
                           2. Nueva cuenta
